Titolo: KKnD (video game)

Anno: 1997

Descrizione: KKnD, or Krush, Kill 'n' Destroy is the first of three real-time strategy games in the KKnD series, and was released on March 5, 1997. The game takes place in a post-apocalyptic setting, where two factions are fighting for control over the few natural resources left. Each faction has its own campaign consisting of 15 missions each, and there is also a multiplayer mode which allows up to 6 people to play via LAN or modem/serial connection.
KKnD: Xtreme is an improved and extended version of KKnD, released on October 30, 1997.The successor, KKND2: Krossfire, was released in 1998.